Albert Dekker https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Albert_Dekker 0 Albert Dekker (born Thomas Albert Ecke Van Dekker, December 20, 1905 – May 5, 1968) was an American character actor and politician best known for his roles in Dr. Cyclops, The Killers, Kiss Me Deadly, and The Wild Bunch. He is sometimes credited as Albert Van Dekker or Albert van Dekker.
